ass=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/01 8:05:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eqiceni.co.uk/members/sarxossmall1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> Its for class balancing, so they should be buyable at vendors like they did with druids and mages. If they make them a quest, it will just piss off the majority of wizards. Even making them a drop in WW or SS would be stupid, because then we'd have to kill the very mobs that gate, which we should be anchoring.<br><br>I dont like the look of that 30 second silence period though, 30 seconds of not being able to do anything while the anchor lasts 12 or 18 seconds.<br><br>Sar<br><br>------------------------------<br>Sarxos<br>- [60 Sorcerer], Iceni, Innoruuk<br><br>Silentsong<br>- [54 Minstrel], Iceni, Innoruuk<br>------------------------------<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.kestrelarts.com/images/grimicon.jpg BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/01 8:39:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://dynamic.gamespy.com/~cazic/cazic/ubb/uploads/grimtoo.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> Doubtful, but who knows.  I wish they'd make all new spells research but they have totally dropped that entire concept.  Its sad, because it was a bright spot in the spell system. <p><IMG SRC="http://www.kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg" ></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvexrion2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vexrion2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/01 12:05:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> Wasnt concussion suppse to 'balance out' aggro issues.  Last time I check that wasnt purchasable.<br><br>I expect a time sink quest, one that takes your guild and then some.  <br><br>concusion was a 39th level spell and that quest isnt doable to 48 with massive help.<br><br>Anchors start at 51<br><br>/shudders<br><br>we've always had to work to make ourselves useful other than being a taxi.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwraithwavefeaamael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wraithwave FeaAmael</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://keith.vaughan.home.mindspring.com/img/ball3.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/01 12:13:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://wraithwave.homestead.com/files/Wraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> Concussion is more of a personal preference spell.  You really don't ever need that spell.  If you really want it, you can get it.  I think they are making a much bigger deal of this being a group desire correction than concussion.  But you have a point.  It will be interesting to see how they handle it. <p><img src="http://wraithwave.homestead.com/files/Wraith.gif" border="0"><BR><img src="http://wraithwave.homestead.com/files/Wraith3.gif" border="0"><BR>60th Generation Sorcerer of Cazic - Thule</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uqinadann.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qinadann</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/2/01 11:48:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> I am 99.99% sure it WILL NOT be spells you can buy from vendors, at least the lv 60 one anyway.  Most likely the anchor spell will be mob dropped spell from 1 out of 20 lv 60+ mob that can gate. Then again knowing how much VI hates wiz, they might call it wiz epic spell quest that requires a dozen rare drops from boss mobs in vp and sleeper's tomb. Well we will find out soon enough I guess...<br>Qinadan<br>60th Sorceror - IB<br>Luclin <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uxilet.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xilet</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/10/01 5:17:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> Just like to bring up the fact CoH goes for 10-15k <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwraithwavefeaamael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wraithwave FeaAmael</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://keith.vaughan.home.mindspring.com/img/ball3.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/13/01 8:36:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://wraithwave.homestead.com/files/Wraith.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Will the new &quot;Anchor&quot; spells be quest?</span><hr size=1> Depends on the server.  I can safely say on my server that noone in there right mind would ever pay close to that amount.  No matter how bad they wanted it.  Some servers, money is less of an object than others.  Its all relative though. <p><img src="http://wraithwave.homestead.com/files/Wraith.gif" border="0"><BR><img src="http://wraithwave.homestead.com/files/Wraith3.gif" border="0"><BR>60th Generation Sorcerer of Cazic - Thule</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=mentallo>Mentallo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/4/01 6:52:03 am)</font><br